<br>
For ragefire specifically a sufficient force is required, verent doesn't define sufficient force. <br>
<br>
&quot;or group that is prepared to engage that same NPC without that group's specific permission.&quot;<br>
<br>
TFS was definitly a group that is prepared to engage that same NPC. VD didn't have the forces to win the fight*. And we didn't give them permission to engage. Therefore using verents definition of Kill Stealing they stole it. <br>
